Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.25,0:00:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬萬不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別小瞧我
